data.description: Welcome Home!  Home features endless improvements over the years to include a remodeled eat-in kitchen w/granite counters, Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, refinished white cabinets, tile backsplash and built-in water filtration system; gleaming wood laminate floors throughout the main level; main level powder room; massive owner's suite with walk-in closet; remodeled en suite owner's bathroom with new marble top vanity with double sinks, separate shower with custom tile work and glass doors, soaking tub, Lifeproof vinyl plank flooring, new mirror, and fixtures; updated 2nd full bathroom; 2nd-floor laundry room; low condo fee includes exterior lawn maintenance; 1 assigned parking space and plenty of overflow and visitor spaces; in Columbia, but no CPRA fee.  2.5% VA Assumable Interest Rate. Schedule your appointment today!
